data.description: Serious inquiries only contact me directly at keundrierc2@gmail.com. Pre approvals preferred. Spring home on a quiet cul-de-sac, walking distance from an elementary school, perfect for those with young children.  Updated gray tile floors matching granite counter tops and back splash with breakfast bar for open concept dining & neutral paint colors throughout. New windows and roof within the last three years. Subdivision pool & playground all walking distance and short drive from shopping mall and major highways for easy commute. Won't last long call or email today!
data.whatILove: Nicely tucked away mature home, away from the hustle & bustle of city life, but close enough for a short drive to it all.
